 {"id":"bd-qjl2a","title":"syscall: renameat2 exchange with null newpath should return EFAULT exactly","description":"Host glibc returns EFAULT for renameat2(AT_FDCWD, \".\", AT_FDCWD, NULL, RENAME_EXCHANGE). Add ABI regression coverage so exchange mode preserves the null-destination-path fault.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-21T09:29:12.677915290Z","created_by":"AmberSignal","updated_at":"2026-04-21T09:29:12.677915290Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
